Titolo: Abyss of the Sacrifice

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Abyss of the Sacrifice (密室のサクリファイス, Misshitsu no Sakurifaisu) is a Japanese visual novel adventure game for the PlayStation Portable and by Intense and D3 Publisher. It was released on February 4, 2010. The game is described as a "trap adventure" (トラップアドベンチャー, Torappu Adobenchā). An enhanced version of game for the Nintendo Switch and Microsoft Windows was released worldwide on December 17, 2020.